ADDITIONAL NOTICE - NOT A MEDICAL DEVICE

This software is a personal hobby project and is explicitly NOT a certified,
regulated, or clinically validated medical device. It is provided as a
supplemental monitoring aid only and must never be relied upon as a
substitute for professional medical care, in-person caregiving, nursing
supervision, or emergency services.

The software uses third-party AI image analysis (Anthropic's Claude models),
which can produce incorrect results, including failing to detect real safety
issues (false negatives) and incorrectly flagging non-issues (false
positives). Users assume full responsibility for independently verifying the
software's behavior in their own environment before relying on it in any way,
and for maintaining appropriate human supervision and medical care at all
times regardless of this software's output.

In case of a medical emergency, contact your local emergency services
immediately. Do not wait for, or rely on, a notification from this software.
